values: 缺乏；不足；缺少；短缺；匮乏；欠缺
缺乏；缺少；没有；不足；不具备；欠缺；短缺

word_mean_info__list.difference: 语气较重，指需要必不可少的东西，强调急需。
使用广泛，语气较轻。强调急需时可与need换用，但有时暗示所需的人或物是完成某一任务必不可少的。
指完全短缺或数量不足。
侧重缺少某种必需之物，或个人渴望得到的东西。
指不足，但侧重达不到规定的，需要的或已知应有的数量。
指某物根本不存在或完全短缺，或某人虽存在，但未到现场。
指产量不足或缺乏某物难以应付或满足需要。
普通用词，指部分或完全的不足。
指完全或短缺某物，侧重缺少之物是必需的东西。使用范围比lack窄些。

word_group.brief_definition: 缺乏合作；缺少合作；欠缺合作
缺乏证据；缺少证据；证据缺乏
缺乏经验；缺少经验；经验缺乏
缺乏睡眠；缺少睡眠；睡眠不足
缺乏关注；缺乏注意；缺乏重视
相对缺乏；相对欠缺；相对不足
长期缺乏；长期不足；长期匮乏

bilingual.source: Astronauts' bones and muscles can get very weak in space due to the lack of gravity.
bilingual.target: 由于缺乏重力，宇航员的骨骼和肌肉在太空中会变得非常虚弱。
缺乏睡眠是疲劳的原因。

bilingual.source: The lack of skilled workers has left the industry uncompetitive.
bilingual.target: 缺乏熟练工人使该行业缺乏竞争力。
缺乏睡眠使许多人苦恼。
他的行为缺乏基本的人性。
他的观点缺乏理论基础。

bilingual.source: She feels a lack of motivation lately.
Lack of sleep can ail your health.
bilingual.target: 缺乏睡眠会使痛苦你的健康。

bilingual.source: A lack of erythrocyte can lead to anemia.
bilingual.target: 缺乏红细胞会导致贫血。

bilingual.source: The lack of progress frustrates the team.
bilingual.target: 进展的缺乏使团队沮丧。

list.abstract: 日本男性同人画师、网络画手。创建个人工作室「なんかの」绘制商业性画集。曾将作画过程放于网络上，被国人网友通称为“画工帝”或“海贼王画工帝”。
lack是一个英语单词，名词、动词，作名词时意思是“缺乏，不足”，作动词时意思是“缺乏，缺少，不足，没有；需要”。

yingyinNormal.en: I admit, I lack the imagination to even conceive of someone like you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我承认，我缺乏想象力来构想你这样的人。

yingyinNormal.en: Five points will be taken from Gryffindor for your serious lack of judgment.
yingyinNormal.zh: 格兰芬多将被扣去五分，因为你做事严重缺乏判断。

yingyinNormal.en: What if I get caught? Fear of failure! Lack of confidence! Kind of a wuss!
yingyinNormal.zh: 万一被抓到怎么办？害怕失败！缺乏自信！有点怂逼！

yingyinNormal.en: And the lack of equal opportunity keeps all of us from failing our true potential.
yingyinNormal.zh: 缺乏平等机会让我们所有人无法发挥自己的真正潜能。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: So? So, lack of a physiological response while lying is characteristic of a violent sociopath.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以说？所以说，你撒谎时缺乏生理反应，这是反社会暴力狂的特点。

yingyinNormal.en: And due to a lack of foresight on part of one of my predecessors, 35 years of information, raw information, exists here. Nowhere else.
yingyinNormal.zh: 由于我的某个前任缺乏远见，35年来的资料，原始资料，都在这里，别的地方都没有。

yingyinNormal.en: I will demonstrate that I was improperly instructed in driving by a woman whose lack of respect for society borders on the sociopathic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要论证的是，我在驾驶过程中受到一个女人的误导，这个女人缺乏社会上对反社会界定的基本认识。

yingyinNormal.en: When I was going through all my insecurities And uncertainty and lack of confidence, I was losing focus on god. I was focusing on all these other things, Like my job and what other people thought of me And what the reporters were writing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我感到缺乏安全感，失去信心，那是因为我分散了对神的专注，我把注意力放到别的事情上了，比如我的工作和别人的想法以及各种对我的报道

yingyinNormal.en: Like clones? No. Clones lack genetic plasticity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就跟克隆一样？不，克隆还缺少基因可塑性。

yingyinNormal.en: You, lack all honor!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不值得信任。

yingyinNormal.en: And you had no contact with Medivh since? Not for the lack of trying.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自那之后就没再联系上麦迪文了？试过很多次了。

yingyinNormal.en: How is this maritime salvage? Other than the lack of water, how is it not?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这怎么符合海难救助法？除了没有水，怎么不符合？

yingyinNormal.en: I knew Theresa well. If she had any faults, a lack of loyalty wasn't one of them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很了解特蕾莎，就算她有缺点，但绝不会不忠诚。

yingyinNormal.en: That lack of oxygen will slow down your decay and give you more time to fossilize.
yingyinNormal.zh: 缺氧会减缓你尸体的腐烂给你更多时间变成化石。

yingyinNormal.en: The lack of gravity did decompress my spine, so I'm like an inch and a half taller.
yingyinNormal.zh: 失重状态拉松了我的脊柱，所以我高了3.8厘米。

yingyinNormal.en: How did you notice that? I lack the arrogance to ignore details, I'm not the police.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么看到的？我没有你们警方那种无视细节的自大。

yingyinNormal.en: No matter the policy question, foreign or domestic, we hammer Dunbar's lack of experience.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不论是政策，国际或国内问题，我们都抨击邓巴经验不足。

yingyinNormal.en: My suspicion of Marco has waned, but for now, to be safe, those whom lack your trust kill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经不再怀疑马可，但是安全起见，对于您不信任的人，还是杀了吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Comes to us all, master Wayne. Even you got too old to die young. And not for lack of trying.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人人都会老，韦恩少爷，你也到了死掉也称不上英年早逝的年纪了，并不是说你没试过。

yingyinNormal.en: They were clever, Leonard. They exploited my complete lack of interest in what you were doing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们油菜啊，莱纳德，他们完全明白我对你那些破事儿一点兴趣没有。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the state of being without or not having enough of something

examination_example.sentence: Students are usually to blame for their <highlight>lack</highlight> of resources.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 学生通常因缺乏资源而受到责备。

examination_example.sentence: Stereotypes associated with obesity include laziness, <highlight>lack</highlight> of will power, and lower prospects for success.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与肥胖相关的刻板印象包括懒惰、缺乏意志力和较低的成功可能性。

examination_example.sentence: Social scientists who complain about a <highlight>lack</highlight> of funding should not expect more in today's economic climate.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在今天的经济环境下，抱怨资金短缺的社会科学家不应该有更多的期待。

word_usage.usage: lack作动词时，为及物动词，其后可接名词或者代词，如：lack food，不可用于被动结构，也不用于进行时。
lack作名词时，常用单数形式，其后常跟of sth.，如：a lack of food

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the state of being without or not having enough of something

examination_example.sentence: What they sometimes <highlight>lack</highlight> is feedback from the people who they hope will use their products.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有时缺乏的是他们希望使用他们的产品的人的反馈。

examination_example.sentence: As around 75% of the local harvest goes to waste thanks to a <highlight>lack</highlight> of proper storage facilities.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于缺乏适当的储存设施，当地约75%的收成都被浪费了。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 指完全短缺或数量不足。
语气较重, 指需要必不可少的东西, 强调急需。

sense_info_list.en: the state of being without or not having enough of something

examination_example.sentence: People from different races, genders, and regions all suffer from a <highlight>lack</highlight> of financial security.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 来自不同种族、性别和地区的人都缺乏经济保障。

examination_example.sentence: Another worker said the <highlight>lack</highlight> of protection at the store made her feel uncomfortable at work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 另一名工人说，商店里缺乏保护让她在工作中感到不舒服。

examination_example.sentence: According to the public, at least, it's not that they <highlight>lack</highlight> toughness, management talent or proper skill sets. It's also not all about work-life balance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 至少公众认为，这并不是因为他们缺乏韧性、管理才能或适当的技能。这也不全是工作与生活平衡的问题。

sense_info_list.en: the state of being without or not having enough of something

examination_example.sentence: A tight schedule is no excuse for <highlight>lack</highlight> of action.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 紧凑的计划不是行动不足的借口。

examination_example.sentence: In Mohan's opinion, what human quality is <highlight>lacking</highlight> in digital beings?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在Mohan看来，数字生物缺少什么样的人类品质？

examination_example.sentence: This is what motivation or the <highlight>lack</highlight> of it can do.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是动机或缺乏动机所能做的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the state of being without or not having enough of something

examination_example.sentence: These weren’t stopped by their age or size or <highlight>lack</highlight> of resources.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些并没有因为它们的年龄、规模或缺乏资源而停止。

examination_example.sentence: This <highlight>lack</highlight> of regular physical activity means people burn fewer calories than in the past.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 缺乏规律的体育活动意味着人们比过去消耗更少的卡路里。

examination_example.sentence: Sometimes teens <highlight>lack</highlight> sleep because of after-school jobs that are taken on to earn extra money for college, family expenses, or simply for clothes．
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有时候，青少年睡眠不足是因为他们在课余时间打工赚些额外的钱来支付大学学费、家庭开销，或者仅仅是买衣服。
